1
00:00:15,207 --> 00:00:16,717
Hero!

2
00:00:22,047 --> 00:00:24,217
Hero!

3
00:00:24,217 --> 00:00:25,907
Take me with you!

4
00:00:25,907 --> 00:00:27,507
Move this thing! Now!

5
00:00:35,437 --> 00:00:38,187
I am never traveling with you again!

6
00:00:38,187 --> 00:00:40,797
Aw don't be like that. 
You're making me sad.

7
00:00:40,797 --> 00:00:43,527
We haven't even reached the mine yet.

8
00:00:43,527 --> 00:00:47,037
Then stop making trouble every 
single day you worthless hero!

9
00:00:58,037 --> 00:00:58,937
Beautiful.

10
00:00:59,537 --> 00:01:01,077
It suits you well.

11
00:01:01,077 --> 00:01:03,567
I think this is what you 
should wear on the big day.

12
00:01:03,567 --> 00:01:07,297
I think what I usually wear 
would be just fine though...

13
00:01:07,857 --> 00:01:09,047
That won't do.

14
00:01:09,627 --> 00:01:13,177
Your attire must befit 
the Aquaraine family.

15
00:01:13,177 --> 00:01:15,887
Isn't this a bit too extravagant?

16
00:01:17,357 --> 00:01:19,097
You dislike it?

17
00:01:22,847 --> 00:01:26,857
Pardon me. There's a visitor for milady.

18
00:01:30,187 --> 00:01:31,867
Thank you for waiting.

19
00:01:32,227 --> 00:01:34,067
Sorry to come without warning.

20
00:01:34,067 --> 00:01:37,747
I wanted to ask you something 
about healing magic...

21
00:01:38,317 --> 00:01:40,767
Wait why are you dressed like that?

22
00:01:41,297 --> 00:01:43,497
It looks weird doesn't it?

23
00:01:43,497 --> 00:01:46,757
Of course not! You look super pretty.

24
00:01:46,757 --> 00:01:52,757
I was just surprised because I so 
rarely see you dressed like a noble.

25
00:01:53,267 --> 00:01:55,767
I have an arranged marriage meeting.

26
00:01:56,207 --> 00:01:57,447
Ah I see.

27
00:01:57,447 --> 00:01:59,767
Wait what?!

28
00:02:00,017 --> 00:02:03,767
Are you serious?! I mean 
are you... sure about this?

29
00:02:03,767 --> 00:02:07,627
I'm only meeting him once 
per His Majesty's orders.

30
00:02:07,627 --> 00:02:09,557
I don't intend to marry him.

31
00:02:09,557 --> 00:02:12,237
I'm still training after all.

32
00:02:12,517 --> 00:02:15,927
Training? How studious can you be?

33
00:02:15,927 --> 00:02:18,247
So when are you meeting the guy?

34
00:02:18,247 --> 00:02:19,967
In three days.

35
00:02:19,967 --> 00:02:21,247
Who is he?

36
00:02:21,247 --> 00:02:24,047
He's someone you know.

37
00:02:24,497 --> 00:02:28,507
A member of the hero's party 
of the Duchy of Luminaria.

38
00:02:28,507 --> 00:02:32,007
I am honored to have 
this audience with you.

39
00:02:33,267 --> 00:02:36,897
My name is Soleil Graceheart.

40
00:04:11,307 --> 00:04:12,527
Miss Cecilia.

41
00:04:14,667 --> 00:04:16,047
It's good to see you again.

42
00:04:22,757 --> 00:04:24,497
I believe the last time we met

43
00:04:24,497 --> 00:04:27,007
was at the party celebrating 
the defeat of the Demon King.

44
00:04:27,867 --> 00:04:29,327
Yes I believe so.

45
00:04:31,897 --> 00:04:33,887
King Dartz told me

46
00:04:34,257 --> 00:04:37,117
that you aren't interested in marriage

47
00:04:37,117 --> 00:04:39,717
and have turned down 
all proposals thus far.

48
00:04:42,457 --> 00:04:45,267
I'm still training after all.

49
00:04:48,937 --> 00:04:50,697
These are fine tea leaves.

50
00:04:50,697 --> 00:04:51,407
Huh?

51
00:04:52,097 --> 00:04:55,037
And it's because you 
defeated the Demon King

52
00:04:55,507 --> 00:04:58,677
that we can enjoy such delicious tea now.

53
00:04:59,037 --> 00:05:02,537
It wasn't me. It was all the hero.

54
00:05:02,857 --> 00:05:07,037
But I'm sure he'd say it was 
all of us who made it possible.

55
00:05:08,347 --> 00:05:09,307
True.

56
00:05:09,307 --> 00:05:13,027
And that's probably why he was 
able to become a true hero.

57
00:05:13,557 --> 00:05:14,297
That said...

58
00:05:14,987 --> 00:05:16,917
there are some heroes

59
00:05:16,917 --> 00:05:20,047
who are chosen to challenge the Demon 
King solely for their strength.

60
00:05:21,577 --> 00:05:25,557
You know about Miller the hero 
of the Gallis Empire yes?

61
00:05:25,837 --> 00:05:26,657
Yes.

62
00:05:27,337 --> 00:05:29,687
This is only a rumor

63
00:05:29,687 --> 00:05:32,387
but I hear he's imprisoned 
in the empire now.

64
00:05:32,997 --> 00:05:34,567
That's a shame.

65
00:05:35,307 --> 00:05:39,067
So why does each nation 
have its own hero's party?

66
00:05:39,457 --> 00:05:44,577
I'm sure you... no anyone who's 
a noble must have an inkling.

67
00:05:48,667 --> 00:05:51,907
Because even as humanity was 
being wiped out by demons

68
00:05:52,467 --> 00:05:56,217
the kings of each nation competed 
for supremacy in the aftermath.

69
00:05:56,947 --> 00:06:01,217
Why can't people just work hand in hand?

70
00:06:02,607 --> 00:06:04,347
I feel the same way.

71
00:06:05,177 --> 00:06:09,177
But thankfully King Dartz is a wise man.

72
00:06:10,057 --> 00:06:13,727
He is quite concerned about the signs 
of conflict in our neighbor nations.

73
00:06:14,137 --> 00:06:18,437
That must be why he accepted my proposal.

74
00:06:19,247 --> 00:06:20,447
What do you mean?

75
00:06:21,097 --> 00:06:23,807
Our marriage will make 
it known far and wide

76
00:06:23,807 --> 00:06:29,567
that the Duchy of Luminaria and the 
Kingdom of Clariness are friends.

77
00:06:30,367 --> 00:06:34,097
It will keep any countries with 
malicious intentions in check.

78
00:06:38,187 --> 00:06:39,547
Miss Cecilia...

79
00:06:40,377 --> 00:06:43,567
Please do me the honor of marrying me.

80
00:06:44,267 --> 00:06:45,557
And then

81
00:06:46,687 --> 00:06:49,297
let us guide this world 
toward peace together.

82
00:06:53,557 --> 00:06:55,367
Check this out.

83
00:06:55,367 --> 00:06:56,737
Are you kidding me?

84
00:06:56,737 --> 00:06:58,237
This is...

85
00:07:02,347 --> 00:07:06,117
We ran into a monster nest 
while we were mining.

86
00:07:06,377 --> 00:07:08,127
They're so cute.

87
00:07:08,127 --> 00:07:09,597
So cute.

88
00:07:10,117 --> 00:07:11,837
It's a real problem.

89
00:07:11,837 --> 00:07:15,037
I can't risk using my pickaxe now.

90
00:07:15,037 --> 00:07:18,767
Which is why I asked an 
official to contact the hero.

91
00:07:18,767 --> 00:07:23,007
Could you please do something 
about this without hurting them?

92
00:07:23,277 --> 00:07:26,217
Got it! Leave this to us!

93
00:07:28,987 --> 00:07:31,157
What do you think we should do Yoki?

94
00:07:31,937 --> 00:07:33,347
Why are you asking me?

95
00:07:33,687 --> 00:07:37,187
You're the one who accepted the 
quest with total confidence.

96
00:07:37,187 --> 00:07:38,317
Yep!

97
00:07:38,317 --> 00:07:41,827
You always give me good advice

98
00:07:41,827 --> 00:07:44,747
so I figured you'd have a 
good idea this time too!

99
00:07:45,257 --> 00:07:45,987
Dude.

100
00:07:46,617 --> 00:07:49,107
You seriously have no ideas at all?!

101
00:07:58,397 --> 00:08:02,007
I'm sorry. This is all 
far too much for me.

102
00:08:02,307 --> 00:08:06,517
It would seem you don't understand 
the significance of your own standing.

103
00:08:08,357 --> 00:08:12,517
I made some big talk but I 
am still inexperienced myself.

104
00:08:12,997 --> 00:08:14,767
I'm still training.

105
00:08:15,107 --> 00:08:18,097
Let's put the marriage discussion 
aside for the moment.

106
00:08:20,157 --> 00:08:23,837
The truth is I've been staying 
in Minerva for some time now.

107
00:08:24,237 --> 00:08:27,417
I'm in the midst of learning about 
this country and its people.

108
00:08:27,417 --> 00:08:30,037
And... why is that?

109
00:08:30,687 --> 00:08:34,617
Nobles such as you and I need to have 
an understanding of other countries.

110
00:08:35,267 --> 00:08:39,557
If more nations understood each 
other more wars could be avoided.

111
00:08:41,097 --> 00:08:44,547
So I ask this favor of you...

112
00:08:45,087 --> 00:08:47,857
Any time that is convenient 
for you will do.

113
00:08:48,227 --> 00:08:49,557
Would you please...

114
00:08:50,047 --> 00:08:53,557
teach me more about this country?

115
00:08:58,047 --> 00:08:59,407
All right.

116
00:09:01,087 --> 00:09:02,277
Thank you!

117
00:09:02,567 --> 00:09:06,147
I can see that you have 
very good intentions.

118
00:09:07,057 --> 00:09:10,257
If it will lead us to friendlier 
relations with the Duchy of Luminaria

119
00:09:10,827 --> 00:09:12,657
I would be happy to help.

120
00:09:19,557 --> 00:09:21,587
Can I ask for your advice?

121
00:09:22,337 --> 00:09:24,117
Sure I guess.

122
00:09:24,627 --> 00:09:28,037
It's about Cecilia's arranged marriage...

123
00:09:28,397 --> 00:09:29,337
Huh?

124
00:09:29,967 --> 00:09:31,097
What did you just say?!

125
00:09:31,477 --> 00:09:33,847
Wait you didn't know about it?

126
00:09:38,707 --> 00:09:42,607
I was so shocked that I went to see her...

127
00:09:43,097 --> 00:09:46,737
Cecilia! You can't go through with 
an arranged marriage! Tell them no!

128
00:09:46,737 --> 00:09:49,707
The king ordered me to.

129
00:09:49,707 --> 00:09:53,737
You just can't! Tell them 
you won't do it Cecilia!

130
00:09:53,737 --> 00:09:58,267
Yuga if you're going to throw a 
tantrum do it in front of the king.

131
00:10:01,777 --> 00:10:03,887
I don't want her to have 
an arranged marriage.

132
00:10:03,887 --> 00:10:06,097
And it's with Soleil no less.

133
00:10:06,097 --> 00:10:07,467
Soleil?

134
00:10:07,467 --> 00:10:11,007
He's in the hero's party 
of the Duchy of Luminaria.

135
00:10:11,007 --> 00:10:13,347
He's about as good with 
the sword as Raven.

136
00:10:13,897 --> 00:10:18,227
He's the heir to an influential lord 
he's smart he has impeccable manners...

137
00:10:18,227 --> 00:10:21,857
Sorry. You'll have to try to 
finish the quest on your own.

138
00:10:22,427 --> 00:10:23,077
Huh?

139
00:10:23,677 --> 00:10:25,017
Yoki?

140
00:10:41,247 --> 00:10:45,247
Why... didn't she tell me?

141
00:10:54,507 --> 00:10:55,657
Why?!

142
00:11:11,157 --> 00:11:13,707
Can we help you miss?

143
00:11:13,707 --> 00:11:16,447
Um... I-Is Yuga...

144
00:11:16,907 --> 00:11:18,657
Mikana!

145
00:11:18,657 --> 00:11:20,697
I'm so glad you're here!

146
00:11:20,697 --> 00:11:23,567
I was really stuck! I 
can't handle this alone!

147
00:11:23,897 --> 00:11:26,417
Alone? Where's the civilian?

148
00:11:26,417 --> 00:11:29,167
Yoki just up and went back home.

149
00:11:29,427 --> 00:11:30,767
Why?

150
00:11:30,767 --> 00:11:33,387
We were talking about Cecilia's 
arranged marriage and—

151
00:11:34,777 --> 00:11:36,927
Yuga! You knew about that?

152
00:11:36,927 --> 00:11:40,107
Oh good! You knew about it too!

153
00:11:41,597 --> 00:11:44,777
What does he think he's going to do?

154
00:11:51,477 --> 00:11:53,257
This is the orphanage.

155
00:11:54,497 --> 00:11:56,047
Holy Mother!

156
00:11:57,467 --> 00:12:00,147
I baked cookies for all of you today.

157
00:12:00,147 --> 00:12:01,487
Here they are.

158
00:12:01,487 --> 00:12:03,037
Yay! Cookies!

159
00:12:03,347 --> 00:12:05,997
Guys you have to say thank 
you to the Holy Mother!

160
00:12:06,267 --> 00:12:10,267
Thank you Holy Mother!

161
00:12:10,717 --> 00:12:13,387
Make sure you share them okay?

162
00:12:13,387 --> 00:12:15,327
Okay!

163
00:12:17,147 --> 00:12:19,527
Holy Mother! Tell us a story!

164
00:12:19,527 --> 00:12:21,427
Aw I'd rather draw pictures!

165
00:12:22,017 --> 00:12:24,747
Easy now. Remember to take turns.

166
00:12:24,747 --> 00:12:26,267
Let's eat the cookies first.

167
00:12:26,267 --> 00:12:28,477
Who are you mister?

168
00:12:29,137 --> 00:12:31,737
I am the Holy Mother's helper.

169
00:12:31,737 --> 00:12:33,487
Soleil!

170
00:12:33,887 --> 00:12:38,027
It's true. I only hope 
there's some way I can help.

171
00:12:39,487 --> 00:12:41,497
Raise me up high!

172
00:12:42,147 --> 00:12:44,497
Up... high?

173
00:12:44,877 --> 00:12:46,887
What does that mean?

174
00:12:46,887 --> 00:12:48,597
You don't know?

175
00:12:48,597 --> 00:12:50,217
But you're a grown-up.

176
00:12:50,217 --> 00:12:51,507
That's weird!

177
00:12:51,777 --> 00:12:55,507
Soleil pick her up with both hands.

178
00:12:57,227 --> 00:12:58,747
Pardon me then.

179
00:12:59,757 --> 00:13:02,077
Now lift her up high.

180
00:13:02,577 --> 00:13:04,727
L-Like this?

181
00:13:06,827 --> 00:13:09,687
Wow! I'm way up high!

182
00:13:09,927 --> 00:13:11,097
Lucky!

183
00:13:11,097 --> 00:13:12,357
Me next!

184
00:13:12,357 --> 00:13:13,397
Then me!

185
00:13:13,667 --> 00:13:15,547
Come on please!

186
00:13:15,547 --> 00:13:17,907
I'm sorry Soleil.

187
00:13:18,537 --> 00:13:23,427
Don't tire yourself out but could you 
please do the same for the others?

188
00:13:25,857 --> 00:13:27,167
All right.

189
00:13:27,427 --> 00:13:30,607
Let's take turns then shall we?

190
00:13:30,607 --> 00:13:32,657
Yay!

191
00:13:40,627 --> 00:13:45,747
Soleil thank you for your help. 
The children were delighted.

192
00:13:45,747 --> 00:13:49,597
Not at all. I should thank you 
for the valuable experience.

193
00:13:50,117 --> 00:13:53,697
I had no idea children played that way.

194
00:13:54,107 --> 00:13:57,317
They don't in the Duchy of Luminaria?

195
00:13:57,317 --> 00:13:58,857
I'm not sure.

196
00:13:59,497 --> 00:14:01,777
As the heir to the Graceheart family

197
00:14:01,777 --> 00:14:04,867
I spent my childhood studying 
and training with the sword.

198
00:14:05,547 --> 00:14:08,307
I still study under my father every day.

199
00:14:08,307 --> 00:14:11,117
I never have opportunities 
to interact with our people.

200
00:14:11,697 --> 00:14:16,757
So when I was chosen for the hero's party 
and set out to slay the Demon King

201
00:14:16,757 --> 00:14:18,377
every little thing surprised me.

202
00:14:18,947 --> 00:14:21,497
The other members laughed so loudly

203
00:14:21,497 --> 00:14:23,887
they'd get angry and they were so honest.

204
00:14:24,587 --> 00:14:29,007
Interacting with them directly made 
me want to protect them all the more.

205
00:14:29,777 --> 00:14:32,897
From the Demon King and from 
any struggles they may face.

206
00:14:33,137 --> 00:14:35,777
Protect them?

207
00:14:37,147 --> 00:14:39,147
Is that presumptuous of me?

208
00:14:39,147 --> 00:14:42,997
No that's how I've always 
tried to be as well.

209
00:14:42,997 --> 00:14:44,157
And...

210
00:14:45,077 --> 00:14:49,167
I have asked someone with 
great power for help at times.

211
00:14:50,197 --> 00:14:55,127
Now though he helps people in 
need without even being asked.

212
00:14:55,577 --> 00:14:57,917
He sounds wonderful.

213
00:14:58,387 --> 00:14:59,377
Yes.

214
00:14:59,617 --> 00:15:04,637
I want to become worthy 
of standing by his side.

215
00:15:06,817 --> 00:15:09,957
I have a role model as well.

216
00:15:10,277 --> 00:15:12,027
You do?

217
00:15:12,537 --> 00:15:13,147
Yes.

218
00:15:14,857 --> 00:15:17,897
Then I guess we both still 
have a long way to go!

219
00:15:18,527 --> 00:15:19,907
Very true.

220
00:15:22,057 --> 00:15:24,107
Thank you for today

221
00:15:24,107 --> 00:15:29,157
and I hope you'll teach me more tomorrow 
about this country and its people.

222
00:15:29,507 --> 00:15:31,667
I'm happy to do anything I can.

223
00:15:34,317 --> 00:15:35,857
Thank you.

224
00:15:36,917 --> 00:15:38,957
Well then see you tomorrow.

225
00:15:42,267 --> 00:15:45,927
What in the world am I doing?!

226
00:15:47,007 --> 00:15:51,177
I just... couldn't turn him down...

227
00:15:58,957 --> 00:16:03,777
I'm working hard as an adventurer 
now and once I make a decent living

228
00:16:03,777 --> 00:16:06,977
I'm planning to ask her again so...

229
00:16:11,037 --> 00:16:16,097
Yoki seems to be having a lot of fun 
now that he's made so many friends.

230
00:16:16,097 --> 00:16:20,307
He's not the same Yoki who couldn't 
leave the Demon King's castle.

231
00:16:21,427 --> 00:16:24,287
I'm sure... he doesn't 
feel the same about...

232
00:16:35,467 --> 00:16:39,567
I'll make myself invisible 
and go straight to her!

233
00:16:40,137 --> 00:16:41,067
Vanish Wave!

234
00:16:52,907 --> 00:16:54,747
Blue fire?

235
00:16:55,187 --> 00:16:56,097
Yah!

236
00:17:14,427 --> 00:17:17,567
I wasn't expecting to run 
into a demon on my patrol.

237
00:17:17,987 --> 00:17:21,117
Were you trying to hunt humans 
down under cover of night?

238
00:17:21,117 --> 00:17:23,227
Who are you?!

239
00:17:23,227 --> 00:17:24,707
I am...

240
00:17:25,457 --> 00:17:28,847
the Beast of Blue Fire!

241
00:17:29,047 --> 00:17:30,737
BEAST OF BLUE FIRE

242
00:17:30,737 --> 00:17:33,747
The Beast of... Blue Fire?

243
00:17:34,137 --> 00:17:37,707
I incinerate evil with 
the flames of justice!

244
00:17:40,017 --> 00:17:42,497
I don't have time for you right now!

245
00:17:42,837 --> 00:17:45,717
Why bother showing up here now demon?!

246
00:17:54,737 --> 00:17:57,457
What am I even gonna do when I see her?

247
00:17:57,877 --> 00:17:59,037
You will not escape!

248
00:18:05,157 --> 00:18:06,347
He erased it?!

249
00:18:07,197 --> 00:18:08,817
What's going on?!

250
00:18:09,087 --> 00:18:11,247
You're the guy on the wanted posters!

251
00:18:11,247 --> 00:18:13,577
Hey isn't that a demon?

252
00:18:13,577 --> 00:18:15,497
There's a demon!

253
00:18:15,497 --> 00:18:16,537
What's it doing here?!

254
00:18:18,787 --> 00:18:23,457
That's right! Don't let that 
demon take one step into Minerva!

255
00:18:23,837 --> 00:18:24,767
Get lost!

256
00:18:24,767 --> 00:18:25,217
Damn demon!

257
00:18:25,217 --> 00:18:26,547
What'd you come here for?!

258
00:18:50,107 --> 00:18:51,897
C-Come in.

259
00:18:53,297 --> 00:18:54,497
Pardon me.

260
00:18:56,397 --> 00:19:00,787
Milady my husband showed me this.

261
00:19:14,227 --> 00:19:18,597
Why did I have to reincarnate as a demon?

262
00:19:22,957 --> 00:19:25,317
This is one of Kramen's...

263
00:19:30,267 --> 00:19:30,987
Huh?!

264
00:19:37,227 --> 00:19:40,187
This is... Yoki?

265
00:19:41,967 --> 00:19:46,377
The Magic Swordsman of Black 
Lightning... on a wanted poster?!

266
00:19:48,877 --> 00:19:52,627
A demon attempted to infiltrate 
Minerva last night.

267
00:19:53,087 --> 00:19:55,107
Thankfully we fought it off

268
00:19:55,107 --> 00:19:58,107
but we will increase 
patrols and remain alert.

269
00:19:58,107 --> 00:20:00,557
Stay focused all of you!

270
00:20:01,177 --> 00:20:04,147
And that concludes our captain's speech.

271
00:20:04,517 --> 00:20:05,347
Yes sir!

272
00:20:05,347 --> 00:20:06,897
Opening the gate!

273
00:20:14,787 --> 00:20:17,447
Shouldn't we check each 
of them individually?

274
00:20:17,677 --> 00:20:21,277
The demon that showed 
up had horns and wings.

275
00:20:21,277 --> 00:20:24,577
Anyone who doesn't appear 
obviously suspicious is fine.

276
00:20:31,087 --> 00:20:32,367
That's...

277
00:20:32,367 --> 00:20:33,507
Yoki?!

278
00:20:37,177 --> 00:20:38,627
Cecilia?!

279
00:20:39,077 --> 00:20:40,267
Miss Cecilia.

280
00:20:40,267 --> 00:20:41,637
Soleil?

281
00:20:41,637 --> 00:20:44,637
Am I imagining it or is he...

282
00:20:44,637 --> 00:20:46,977
Um... it's all right!

283
00:20:47,717 --> 00:20:49,357
I know him!

284
00:20:50,067 --> 00:20:52,317
How did you get hurt?!

285
00:20:59,017 --> 00:21:00,697
Hold still please!

286
00:21:01,117 --> 00:21:01,887
Okay...

287
00:21:06,367 --> 00:21:07,917
What happened?

288
00:21:11,267 --> 00:21:13,757
Are you finished healing 
him Miss Cecilia?

289
00:21:15,277 --> 00:21:17,677
You said that you know him.

290
00:21:17,677 --> 00:21:21,247
Oh... I'm sorry. Yoki is...

291
00:21:21,247 --> 00:21:23,017
Just a guy she knows in passing.

292
00:21:23,907 --> 00:21:26,787
I'm an adventurer she's helped out a lot.

293
00:21:27,297 --> 00:21:29,927
Cecilia is kind to everyone after all.

294
00:21:29,927 --> 00:21:32,437
She even helps a guy like me.

295
00:21:34,437 --> 00:21:35,997
I see.

296
00:21:35,997 --> 00:21:39,777
I haven't introduced myself. 
I am Soleil Graceheart.

297
00:21:40,277 --> 00:21:42,697
I am hoping to become 
Miss Cecilia's fiancé.

298
00:21:44,667 --> 00:21:47,887
Yoki um... I didn't tell 
you about this but...

299
00:21:48,287 --> 00:21:50,877
Sorry for getting in the way 
of your marriage meeting.

300
00:21:52,307 --> 00:21:54,797
Well have a good day.

301
00:22:01,257 --> 00:22:05,477
We've had a bit of an incident. 
I'll need you to cooperate.

302
00:22:05,477 --> 00:22:06,517
Huh?

303
00:22:09,247 --> 00:22:11,977
Irene stay on watch over here.

304
00:22:12,607 --> 00:22:14,437
Y-Yes sir!

305
00:22:15,067 --> 00:22:21,327
Look I'm at my height 
of seriousness here.

306
00:22:28,327 --> 00:22:31,617
Translation: Rebecca Cottrill
Timing: Andy Ellis

307
00:22:35,027 --> 00:22:38,327
Editing: Ashley Barboza
